</svg></div></div><div class="usp-card is__2" data-floatcard-2=""><h3 class="h4">Coffee Husk</h3><div style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; margin-top: -0.5rem; font-weight: 600; opacity: 0.8;">Fragrance of coffee</div><img src="/coffee huk.png" alt="Coffee Husk Material" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem; width: 100%; height: 260px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 12px; position: relative; z-index: 10;" /><p>Most people wake up to the invigorating fragrance of coffee, making it the most popular beverage worldwide. However, coffee production generates a massive amount of husk waste. Our products ingeniously repurpose this coffee husk into beautiful, resilient, and natural-feeling essentials. Start every morning with a sustainable choice that gives new life to organic materials.</p><div class="usp-card__graphic w-embed"><svg fill="none" height="100%" viewBox="0 0 437 263" width="100%" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">

