</svg></div></div><div class="usp-card is__2" data-floatcard-3=""><h3 class="h4">Bamboo fibre</h3><div style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; margin-top: -0.5rem; font-weight: 600; opacity: 0.8;">Strength of bamboo</div><img src="/bamboo.png" alt="Bamboo Material" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem; width: 100%; height: 260px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 12px; position: relative; z-index: 10;" /><p>Bamboo is a magical, rapidly renewable plant that grows exceptionally fast and absorbs significantly more CO2 than almost any other species. Known for its incredible durability, its structural strength is often compared to that of steel. By incorporating bamboo fibre into our products, we offer an eco-conscious alternative that minimizes environmental impact while delivering outstanding quality.</p><div class="usp-card__graphic w-embed"><svg fill="none" height="100%" viewBox="0 0 438 318" width="100%" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">


